                "thin glass,  8 inches by 2 inches, supporting a",
                "50 micron thick K-1 or K-2 emulsion composition",
                "manufactured by Ilford of England.",
                " A solid-state detector was used for some confirmatory",
                "measurements as well as for a determination of the",
                "alpha0 excitation function for the purpose of",
                "normalizing the emulsion data."
